Gonopods (Figs 10B, 11
C-D
) with coxite about 1/3 as long as telopodite. Prefemur almost half as long as acropodite. Femorite short and slender, slightly enlarged distad. Solenophore clearly coiled and divided into a large spiniform lamella lateralis and a very distinct and coiled lamella medialis. Solenomere relatively long.
